author: kkolinko
msg: Fix processing of "target", "rel" attributes on links in Documentation.
The "<a>" template in the XSLT is not useful, as nowadays we do not generate separate "printer" versions of the docs. It did not support those attributes on <a> tags.
It is backport of r1590492 from tc7.0.x.
